===Etymology===
From {{och-l|淬|to dip into liquid, to plunge, to temper, to dye, etc.}}, as kingfishers dive underwater to catch fish ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). 

The "blue-green, cyan" > "bright" senses are because of the kingfishers' plumages.

; "death of Xi Jinping"
: From the simplified characters of "Xi" (习) and "to die" (卒), which when combined forms "翠".

